 Olympic Committee spokesman said.\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 940, \"end\": 968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"John\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 880}, {\"ngram\": \"no further comment\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Comment was sought from Senate committee chairman Matt Canavan, who requested Coates's attendance at next week's hearing in Brisbane.\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1010, \"end\": 1016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Senate\", \"score\": 0.999999675706529, \"rank\": 3.242902649349092e-07, \"text\": \"Senate\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Senate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Senate\"}, {\"begin\": 1036, \"end\": 1048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Canavan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matt Canavan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Canavan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Canavan\"}, {\"begin\": 1110, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9999999950503025, \"rank\": 4.939698361130118e-09, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Comment\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 993}, {\"ngram\": \"Coates's attendance\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"next week's hearing\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1106}]}, {\"sentence\": \