\"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"scrutiny\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It'd be great to understand how people like John Coates are actually providing advice to the process, as his focus seems to be on a demonstrated evidence of his new way of delivering the Olympics, which is 'do not build anything',\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1477, \"end\": 1488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_H._Coates\", \"score\": 0.999999982621148, \"rank\": 8.83850175013811e-09, \"text\": \"John Coates\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_H._Coates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_H._Coates\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1471}, {\"ngram\": \"advice\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1533}, {\"ngram\": \"his focus\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"a demonstrated evidence\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1586}, {\"ngram\": \"his new way\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1601}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1628}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now that might be fine for London, Tokyo, Paris, LA - those major cities have had their significant moments of growth, but our city has to double in size by 2040 and we need to be using this moment to deliver the important infrastructure for our future.\\\"\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1703, \"end\": 1709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9991761145075622, \"rank\": 0.0008201018260098207, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1711, \"end\": 1716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Oly